《'''[[王冠_(电视剧)|王冠]]'''》（{{lang-en|''The Crown''}}）是一部英美合作拍攝的[[傳記|傳記]][[歷史劇|歷史]][[電視影集|電視影集]]，由[[彼得·摩根|彼得·摩根]]原創與編劇，並由{{tsl|en|Left Bank Pictures|左岸影業}}為[[Netflix|Netflix]]製作，講述現任英國女王[[伊利沙伯二世|伊利沙伯二世]]統治初期的傳記故事。第一季於2016年11月4日在Netflix上線<ref name="PremiereDate">{{cite web |title=Matt Smith's Netflix drama The Crown gets premiere date |url=https://www.ew.com/article/2016/04/11/matt-smith-netflix-crown-premiere-date |website=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2016-04-12 |first=Dylan |last=Kickham |date=2016-04-11 |archive-date=2016-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414121555/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/04/11/matt-smith-netflix-crown-premiere-date |dead-url=no }}</ref>、第二季於2017年12月8日上線<ref name="Season2Release">{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/the-crown-season-2-premiere-date-first-trailer-1202522364/|title='The Crown' Series 2 Sets Premiere Date, Releases First Trailer|last=Otterson|first=Joe|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=2017-08-10|accessdate=2017-08-10|archive-date=2017-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810162238/http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/the-crown-season-2-premiere-date-first-trailer-1202522364/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、第三季於2019年11月17日上線<ref name="Season3">{{cite web|title='The Crown Series 3 (Finally!) Gets November Premiere Date at Netflix|url=https://tvline.com/2019/08/12/the-crown-season-3-premiere-date-netflix/|last=Iannucci|first=Rebecca|work=[[TVLine|TVLine]]|date=2019-08-12|accessdate=2020-07-09|archive-date=2019-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191031050545/https://tvline.com/2019/08/12/the-crown-season-3-premiere-date-netflix/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、第四季於2020年11月15日上線<ref name="S4Premiere">{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/the-crown-season-4-to-premiere-in-november-on-netflix-1203018414/|title='The Crown': Netflix Sets Premiere Date, Drops First Trailer For Season 4|website=Deadline Hollywood|first=Jake|last=Kanter|date=2020-08-20|accessdate=2020-08-20|archive-date=2020-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820153937/https://deadline.com/2020/08/the-crown-season-4-to-premiere-in-november-on-netflix-1203018414/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而第五季則預計於2022年上線<ref name="SeasonFiveFilming">{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/07/the-crown-season-5-premiere-2022-filming-summer-2021-1202990878/ |title='The Crown' Series 5 Will Not Premiere Until 2022 As Netflix Show Takes Filming Break |work=Deadline Hollywood |first=Jake |last=Kanter |date=2020-07-22 |accessdate=2020-07-22 |archive-date=2020-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200722082953/https://deadline.com/2020/07/the-crown-season-5-premiere-2022-filming-summer-2021-1202990878/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

